title: TUMI V3: Our Lightest Luggage. Ever.
description: Our lightest luggage ever goes as far as you’re willing. V3 raises the bar for design and technology excellence and sets a new standard for the future of travel. Whether you’re off exploring the icy Arctic tundra or navigating the bustling streets of Hong Kong, V3 allows you to journey without boundaries and focus on the experience, not what you’re packing.
